"(define-syntax (make-circuit stx)
  (syntax-parse
    stx
    #:datum-literals (pin part wire layout)
    [(_ (~alt (~optional (pin ext-pin ...) 
                         #:defaults ([(ext-pin 1) null]))
              (~optional (part dv ...)
                         #:defaults ([(dv 1) null]))
              (~optional (wire w ...)
                         #:defaults ([(w 1) null]))
              (~optional (layout l) #:defaults ([l #'#f]))) ...)
     #`(make-circuit0 #:external-pins (ext-pin ...)
                     #:vars (dv ...)
                     #:connect (list w ...)
                     #:layout l
                     )]))"
